{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce mandatory biometric identity cards",
        "additional_details": "Failure to produce a card would mean an individual could be detained and their identity checked to see if they are in the country legally.\r\n \r\nThese cards would be linked to a central database of all individuals legally allowed to be in the country, and their biometric data.\r\n \r\nThis could help make it easier for the authorities to identify and detain those illegally in the country.\r\n",
        "background": "I would like the UK Government to introduce a mandatory biometric identity card system as proof of rights to be in the country legally. Everyone should be required to carry their identity card and produce it on request by the authorities.",
